20. No person shall smoke in any of the following areas of the Hospital-
      (a) a ward;
      (b) an operating theatre;
      (c) the intensive care unit;
      (4 a patient care accommodation and treatment area; and
      ( e ) any place where a "No Smoking" sign is displayed.
